node.text: Love & appreciate @martellofficial for allowing me to share my story & journey with Apartment Bartender 🙏🏽🥃 It’s wild to think back to where things started, back when I didn’t know a thing about how to make an old fashioned, or where the shutter button on my little entry level camera was. I’ve always believed a great drink builds community, and you don’t have to go much further than the comfort of your home to have a great drink experience. Click the link in my bio to read a bit more on my path. Cheers fam! 🥃 #SwiftOnes #Martell #MartellPartner #ApartmentBartender

node.text:
Father’s Day ♥️ The biggest and best surprise of 2020 was finding out that I was going to be a Father. It’s true what they say about your entire life & world changing in an instant, in all the best ways. For the past 9 months, my mind and heart have been completely consumed with gearing my life up to be a Dad. My baby boy entered this world a few weeks ago, and I couldn’t be more in love with him, and with being his Father. I could go on and on about him, but I have a diaper to change 😉 Happy Father’s Day to all the amazing Dad’s out there, both old and new - pouring up a little extra for you today 🙏🏽 #FathersDay
-

🎥: thanks to my incredibly talented friend @planet5films

Celebrating the upcoming holidays with my friends at @hennessy, and mixing up a classic Manhattan cocktail with Hennessy VSOP Privilège. Consider making and sharing this cocktail amongst your family & friends this holiday season. Recipe specs are below. Cheers y’all! 🥃 #Ad #HennessyVSOP
-
• 1.75 oz Hennessy VSOP Privilege
• .75 oz Sweet Vermouth
• 2 dashes of aromatic bitters
-
Combine all ingredients into a mixing glass, and stir with ice. Strain into a chilled coupe glass, and garnish with an orange twist.

node.text: Love & appreciate @martellofficial for allowing me to share my story & journey with Apartment Bartender 🙏🏽🥃 It’s wild to think back to where things started, back when I didn’t know a thing about how to make an old fashioned, or where the shutter button on my little entry level camera was. I’ve always believed a great drink builds community, and you don’t have to go much further than the comfort of your home to have a great drink experience. Click the link in my bio to read a bit more on my path. Cheers fam! 🥃 #SwiftOnes #Martell #MartellPartner #ApartmentBartender
